it’s rare in this life that you meet someone who shaped your whole fookin existence. i felt like i met him last night. i felt like i was on a different planet. he was there and i was with him. it was truly the greatest  moment of my fookin life getting to sing “life on mars” with rock n roll legends and past members of bowie’s band at a concert in his memory. thankyou for everything starman. 🖤⚡️🖤

- @davidbowie @mikegarson @rollinglivestudios @rickwakemanmusic @savethechildren

node.text: so excited to announce ill be playin @socceraid for @unicef_uk on saturday the 4th of september in manchester!!! please please go get tickets it’s such an amazing cause! the right to imagine and play is a privilege every single child should have. it’s up to us try our best to ensure every single child born into this world has a future. come to the game, makes signs, come together n bring the fookin energy. please please give anything you can it does make a difference. i love ya 🖤🩸🖤 (link in bio)

node.text:
TOUR NEWS!!!

OCCUPY THE UK TOUR 2021 🇬🇧 IS HAPPENING !!! i cannot wait to be in a room goin fookin mental with you so soon, so get fookin ready! however, unfortunately due to the ongoing COVID restrictions in Scotland, the Glasgow 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁳󠁣󠁴󠁿 shows have had to be moved to the end of the year. i promise i did everything i could, i just want everyone to be as safe as possible. 

-

THE “LIFE ON MARS 2021 UK TOUR”🇬🇧 IS HAPPENING !!! most of these shows are sold out but there is some tix left so don’t sleep. i have been working on this show for months now it’s gonna be fuckin mad!

-

due to travel restrictions THE “LIFE ON MARS 2021 EUROPEAN TOUR” has had to be postponed to 2022. im so sorry i did everything i could, your safety is my top priority. however, we added some dates (BELGIUM, POLAND, PORTUGAL, FINLAND) and due to crazy demand we upgraded some of the rooms and added extra nights. the tickets for the new shows will go on sale *MONDAY 9am LOCAL TIME* all other dates are on sale NOW!

-

im counting down the minutes till i can see you all again. i have missed you all so fookin much. i truly love you all. for all ticket links and info head to link in my bio.🖤🩸🖤

node.text: this is the moment i first got the black heart tattoo. this is the moment where it all started and i never thought in my wildest dreams this is where we would end up. i just wanted to tell the truth about how i felt and see if anyone felt like me, wanted to be friends or just respond and millions of you did! i am so so honoured to be apart of this with you, i am so proud of what we are and what we represent. you have all truly changed my life forever. this is forever. i truly love you all! HAPPY 3 YEARS “21st CENTURY LIABILITY” 🖤🖤🖤
